attributes.title: THIS IS NOT AN APP
attributes.review:
I downloaded this because I wanted to keep up to date with our president but all I have now is a glitched our phone. The second I downloaded this my phone got so hot and powered off. It took 1 hour to turn it on. Once I did it still had a heat warning on. This app also takes your phone number and send it to telemarketers. My phone hasn’t stopped ringing since it turned back on. Thank god for do not disturb, but that doesn’t take away the hundreds of messages too. Every time I open the app it just closes and turns of my phone for a couple minutes. I can’t delete it and I can’t open it. 

Moral of the story is Trump broke my phone and I do not recommend this app. I want to cry now. Gn.

attributes.title: Gave Me Boils
attributes.review: I downloaded this app thinking I was going to be able to support this almighty president of ours however as I opened the app I began to itch. I put in my telephone number as needed and I started to hear car doors shut outside of my home. I was scrolling the app and boils started to appear on my skin. I looked outside because I started to hear loud speaking and a “Mr.President” IT COULDN’T BE OUR LORD SAVIOR HIMSELF. I proceeded to open my front door to try and see Donald for myself but he laughed at me :( He said “Now look at you. A little child with boils all over her” DADDY DONALD DIDN’T EVEN CARE!!! I asked for his help but he said,”No!! It’s your fault that you downloaded my app” I pleaded for dear daddy Donald’s help but he said he had to tend to the children that he had in cages first. Guys please don’t download this app. :| Daddy Donald will hurt you just as he did me.
